---
// Founder credibility block. Portrait lives at public/images/founder/brenda.png
---

<section class="founder section-paper section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="founder__grid">
      <div class="founder__media">
        <img
          class="founder__img"
          src="/images/founder/brenda.png"
          alt="Brenda, founder and artist behind Balloonia Events"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="founder__copy">
        <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--muted">Meet The Founder</p>
        <h2 class="founder__headline">Hi, I'm Brenda.</h2>
        <p class="founder__body">
          Growing up around my father's furniture remodeling business, I learned to appreciate sharp attention to detail early on. After studying interior design at university and styling events for a local nonprofit, I fell in love with creating immersive atmospheres. There is nothing better than turning a simple, ordinary room into a magical experience. When I am not transforming venues, I am focused on styling my own home, because I truly believe every space deserves to feel like a sanctuary.
        </p>
        <p class="founder__signoff">— Brenda</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founder__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .founder__media {
    position: relative;
  }

  .founder__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .founder__headline {
    font-size: var(--type-h2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .founder__body {
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .founder__body:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .founder__signoff {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .founder__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
